{"tid":1431074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好多香港人仲未知道，今次輸既唔只係你","createTime":"2019-08-08T01:57:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:15:08.000Z","uid":81236,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2843d5b3a5f390619578a208031bebf876fe3940","tid":1431074,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T01:57:49.000Z","msg":"仲有所有真心視香港為家既人<br />\n<br />\n同埋之後既世世代代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道好多連登仔都知<br />\n<br />\n但好多市民都仲未知<br />\n<br />\n大家千祈唔好留係同溫層<br />\n<br />\n你睇連登可能好亢奮<br />\n<br />\n但呢個社會仲有好多人未知咩事<br />\n<br />\n唔好比連登熱門post既現象所欺騙，以為成個香港人都係一致方向<br />\n<br />\n圍喂威係冇用，長久落去會好似政府既官員咁以為一切美好<br />\n<br />\n我地要做既應該係輸出革命...<br />\n我地要做既應該係大量文宣...<br />\n我地要要既應該係比更多人知...<br />\n請問大家做咩放軟哂手腳？"},{"pid":"bbf4d44c315c5f85372d05f6967df4cdb3e6cfce","tid":1431074,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:04:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0341678d9f2d7d6a02b9f53b2456e373d0740a8a","tid":1431074,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:14:04.000Z","msg":"大家唔好再自我感覺良好<br />\n<br />\n同班官有咩分別"},{"pid":"041ad7cf70aa88964a028c58f1cad1cc34e9f5d8","tid":1431074,"uid":127922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:16:00.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">[重回主軸] 副本過後，係時候回到主線「五大訴求，缺一不可」</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dzfxsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dzfxsS</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手推，保持焦點呀!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ec494416a87c6b8b5a9666546b54c4343fb78f2e","tid"